\par Ph\'b9m vi \'aeo \'ae\'e9 \'c8m: (0 }{{\field{\*\fldinst SYMBOL 184 \\f "Symbol" \\s 13}{\fldrslt\f3\fs26}}}{ 100) %RH, gi\'b8 tr\'de \'ae\'e9 chia 1 %RH.
